{
  "texts": [
    "The 'VeChain' project addresses many of these long-standing areas of concern and is already operational.",
    "Still, it would be interesting to have even more automated, machine-controlled supply chains in the future.",
    "For that, we have a very different set of Blockchain solutions-based on IoT systems (Sachdev 2019; Ishmaev 2019; Chanson et al. Sep. 2019; Mozumder et al. 2022; Chamola et al. 2020; Javaid et al. 2020; Nguyen and Ali 2019; Bajoudah et al. 2019).",
    "Using existing IoT Blockchain solutions in the NHS-specific requirements, multiple healthcare functions can be performed simultaneously.",
    "The main concern is the lack of interoperability."
  ]
}